      "title": "More than 4 mn successfully registered for \u2019National Fuel Pass\u2019",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The number of people who have successfully registered themselves to obtain National Fuel Passes has exceeded four million (4,096,824) by last evening, the Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said.",
        "He said the new system was tested at 299 CEYPETCO ffuel stations and 34",
        "Meanwhile, 333 filling stations around the country have fully adopted with the new system and tested its QR system yesterday to complete 92,845 transactions.",
        "Accordingly, 87,652 transactions took place and 299 CPC filling stations and 5,193 transactions were recorded at 34 LIOC filling stations. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
